	values('ur0257957','Engrossing motion picture that features some of the finest editing, cinematography and performances ever. There is a wonderful theme of family that runs through this film and its later sequels. No one is truly judged. Love is unconditional. God is the one who truly judges. Easily, the word masterpiece describes this film, but thats been said by so many...Who am I to argue? Masterpiece is right on the money.',10,'10 June 1999','0068646');
