insert into Reviews
	values('ur8131454','A man is imprisoned for 15 years and is released; now he must find out why he was imprisoned.The film has some realistic and gritty fight scenes as well as a very strange yet alluring special effects; it is brilliantly done and the lead actor is fantastic at portraying the conflicted individual.The film is a shocking to say the least, the end will have you squirming as the truth is revealed about his lover and how far a vengeful enemy will go to destroy his already chaos filled existence.The fight scene in the long hall is still the main attraction though as he hammers and punches his way through endless numbers of enemies; it is beautifully shot and is definitely a must see.',8,'5 February 2008','0364569');
