	values('ur1510857','This is a film that stays with you. Of course theres the brilliant performances but theres more. While other films have taken on old age and dementia, those films took on coping with a significant others condition. The difference here is that the film is from the sufferers perspective. You therefore see these events as if you yourself have dementia. And its stunning how, when you walk away, you know you can.',9,'17 September 2020','10272386');
