	values('ur11750202','Though Im not a war movie fan, I thought Platoon was a solid film.Oliver Stone did a great job at directing, with perfect shots especially during the combat scenes. Great cast, but you can only admire Sheens performance as the rest of the actors is a bit in the background to me. Now on the other hand, I felt the movie could have used some extra dynamic script-wise, because even though it is a good storytelling, it is a bit linear.I rated Platoon 7/10, because Im not fond of war films, but I have to admit it is a solid one that conveys emotion especially through Sheens character.',7,'1 October 2012','0091763');
