	values('ur119287680','Beautifully filmed and everyone hamming it up . Started up promising but then I completely lost the plot.... I was prepared to give it a chance and watched it till the end ....urghh unbearable in parts ...couldnt wait till it finished .Yeah yeah I get the message love can be found in even the worst situations no matter how desperately bad or bleak .Michelle Yeoh great and Jamie Lee Curtis a real treat - she made it tolerable .Not for me am too old ,...or not old enough !Why do I need 600 characters to post ? Unbelievable............................................................................................................................................',3,'3 September 2022','6710474');
